tidy data 개념

데이터 전처리를 위해 패턴화한 데이터

  • 각 변수의 개별 column(열)이 있다.
  • 각 관측치는 row(행)을 구성한다.
  • 각 테이블은 단 하나의 관측기준에 따라 조직된 데이터를 저장한다.
# subset Cars93
Cars93_1 <- Cars93[, 1:8]
str(Cars93_1)

Pipes

  • Chain Operator, Pipe Operator (%>%): Ctrl + Shift + M

  • dataframe %>% dplyr functions %>% …

  • 변수들의 인과관계를 파악하며 순서 유의하기!

Summarise Cases

  • summaries(), summaries_each(), count()

  • input : vectors -> output : single values

  • 데이터의 요약통계량

# na.rm = TRUE : 결측값 제외하여 통계량 계산
Cars93 %>%
summarise(Price_mean = mean(Price, na.rm = TRUE),
          Price_median = median(Price, na.rm = TRUE),
          Price_sd = sd(Price, na.rm = TRUE),
          Price_min = min(Price, na.rm = TRUE),
          Price_max = max(Price, na.rm = TRUE),
          Price_IQR = IQR(Price, na.rm = TRUE),
          Price_sum = sum(Price, na.rm = TRUE))
## Warning: package 'bindrcpp' was built under R version 3.4.4
##   Price_mean Price_median Price_sd Price_min Price_max Price_IQR Price_sum
## 1   19.50968         17.7  9.65943       7.4      61.9      11.1    1814.4
Cars93_2 <- Cars93[c(1:10), c("Manufacturer", "Model", "Type")]
Cars93_2
##    Manufacturer      Model    Type

## 2         Acura     Legend Midsize
## 3          Audi         90 Compact
## 4          Audi        100 Midsize

## 7         Buick    LeSabre   Large
## 8         Buick Roadmaster   Large
## 9         Buick    Riviera Midsize
## 10     Cadillac    DeVille   Large
Cars93_2 %>%
summarise(tot_cnt = n(),
          dist_cnt = n_distinct(Manufacturer),
          First_obs = first(Manufacturer),
          Last_obs = last(Manufacturer),
          Nth_5th_obs = nth(Manufacturer, 5))

summaries_each()

# 여러 변수의 같은 요약통계량을 구하고 싶을 때
summarise_each(Cars93, funs(mean, median, sd), Price, MPG.highway)

Group Cases

group_by()

Cars93 %>%
group_by(Type) %>% summarise(tot_cnt = n(),
                             dist_cnt = n_distinct(Manufacturer),
                             Price_mean = mean(Price, na.rm = T),
                             Price_sd = sd(Price, na.rm = T))

mutate()

# 기존 변수를 이용하여 새로운 변수 만들기(수식을 사용하여)
# input : vectors -> output : vectors as same length of input

Cars93_3 <- Cars93[c(1:10), c("Model", "Max.Price", "Min.Price")]
mutate(Cars93_3, Price_range = Max.Price-Min.Price, Price_Max_Min_ratio = Max.Price/Min.Price)

transmutate()

# mutate와 다른 점: 기존 변수 삭제, 신규 변수만 남겨놓는다
transmute(Cars93_3, Price_range = Max.Price-Min.Price, Price_Max_Min_ratio = Max.Price/Min.Price)

rename()

# 데이터 프레임 변수 이름 바꾸기: new_name = old_name
names(Cars93_1)
## [1] "Manufacturer" "Model"        "Type"         "Min.Price"   
## [5] "Price"        "Max.Price"    "MPG.city"     "MPG.highway"
c <- rename(Cars93_1, 
            New_Manufacturer = Manufacturer, 
            New_Model = Model,
            New_Type = Type,
            New_Min.Price = Min.Price,
            New_Price = Price,
            New_Max.Price = Max.Price,
            New_MPG.city = MPG.city,
            New_MPG.highway = MPG.highway)
